##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       8431 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  8431 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   8431 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  8431 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  8431 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 8431 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   8431 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    8431 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    8431 1451
total cross section.                                              8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
- MT5      : (n,anything) cross section                           8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
MT5 contains the reactions which can not be stored in any other   8431 1451
