- MT2      : Elastic angular distribution                         8431 1451
                                                                  8431 1451
The flag LTT=3 is used to indicate a switch at some high energy,  8431 1451
generally 50 MeV, from a Legendre representation to a tabulated   8431 1451
representation. For incident energies below this energy, the      8431 1451
Legendre coefficients are given on a sufficiently precise energy  8431 1451
grid. They are a sum of calculated Legendre coefficients for      8431 1451
compound nucleus and shape-elastic scattering. For higher         8431 1451
